node.text: @edgeratedr arrives on @wwethebump just days before his Universal Title showdown against @romanreigns at #MITB. Raw Women’s Champion @rhearipley_wwe previews her title defense against @charlottewwe, while two-time WWE Hall of Famer @ricflairnatureboy also stops by to chat.

node.title: Edge, Rhea Ripley and Ric Flair look ahead to MITB: WWE’s The Bump, 7/14/21
